OF THE WORLD

16:21.772 --> 16:23.183
THESE LAST FIVE YEARS.

16:23.274 --> 16:25.231
THINK OF
THIS COUNTRY NOW.

16:25.318 --> 16:26.900
IS THERE
ANOTHER LIKE IT?

16:26.986 --> 16:28.818
YOU HAVEN'T PUT
AN END TO SUFFERING.

16:28.905 --> 16:30.771
THERE'S STILL
MURDERS, ROBBERIES.

16:30.865 --> 16:33.106
