PEOPLE ARE STARVING.

16:33.201 --> 16:35.784
THE SUFFERING MAN
WAS MEANTTO ENDURE.

16:35.870 --> 16:38.237
WE CAUSE MOST
OF OUR OWN GRIEFS.

16:38.331 --> 16:40.072
