FROM HIM.

16:40.166 --> 16:42.123
IT IS THE UNNATURAL
CATASTROPHES,

16:42.210 --> 16:44.952
THE GREAT WARS, THE
OVERWHELMING PESTILENCES

16:45.046 --> 16:49.290
THE WHOLESALE SINNING
THAT WE HAVE STOPPED.

16:49.383 --> 16:52.091
I BELIEVE
YOU, BROTHER.

16:52.178 --> 16:53.543
<i>DO YOU TRULY?</i>

16:53.638 --> 16:55.049
YES.

16:55.139 --> 16:57.301
I ADMIT, I WAS
DOUBTFUL AT FIRST,

16:57.391 --> 16:59.678
BUT YOU'VE CONVINCED
ME, ABSOLUTELY.

16:59.769 --> 17:01.806
I PROMISE TO KEEP
YOUR SECRET.

17:01.896 --> 17:03.682
GOOD, MY SON.

17:03.773 --> 17:06.231
TOMORROW, IF YOU
FEEL WELL ENOUGH,

17:06.317 --> 17:08.604
YOU MAY LEAVE.

17:08.694 --> 17:10.276
IN THE MEANTIME,

17:10.363 --> 17:13.195
BROTHER CHRISTOPHORUS
WILL LOOK AFTER YOU.

17:13.281 --> 17:18.492
PLEASE, GO DIRECTLY
TO HIS ROOM.

17:18.579 --> 17:21.320
GOOD NIGHT, BROTHER.

17:21.415 --> 17:23.326
