18:04.250 --> 18:06.992
HE SAID YOU
WERE THE DEVIL.

18:07.086 --> 18:10.295
[chuckling bitterly] THE DEVIL.
THAT'S GOOD.

18:10.381 --> 18:12.543
THAT'S WONDERFUL.

18:12.633 --> 18:14.624
WHAT A DREAM
FOR AN OLD DEVIL

18:14.719 --> 18:17.336
TO CATCH THE DEVIL
AND LOCK HIM UP.

18:17.430 --> 18:19.091
[scoffs]

18:20.641 --> 18:23.349
YOU DON'T BELIEVE
HIM, DO YOU?

18:23.436 --> 18:25.177
NO, OF COURSE NOT.

18:25.271 --> 18:26.807
THEN HELP ME.

18:26.897 --> 18:29.309
WHY DON'T I JUST GO
GET THE AUTHORITIES?

18:29.400 --> 18:31.812
IT WOULD BE
MY DEATH WARRANT.

18:31.902 --> 18:34.439
