VVHY ARE YOU LOCKING THE DOOR?

19:03.100 --> 19:05.307
TO PROTECT YOU.

19:05.394 --> 19:07.305
REST NOW,
MR. ELLINGTON,

19:07.355 --> 19:10.723
<i>REMEMBER YOU'RE STILL
A VERY SICK MAN.</i>

19:56.237 --> 19:57.978
<i>[thunder]</i>

20:04.912 --> 20:07.279
YOU'VE COME. GOOD!

20:07.373 --> 20:08.704
WHAT DO YOU
WANT ME TO DO?

20:08.791 --> 20:10.907
LIFT OFF
THE WOODEN BOLT.

20:14.630 --> 20:16.132
IS THIS ALL
