20:22.471 --> 20:24.382
MR. ELLINGTON, IN
THE NAME OF MERCY.

20:24.473 --> 20:26.555
IF YOU FAIL NOVV, THEY'LL
KILL BOTH OF US.

20:26.600 --> 20:29.137
DON'T YOU
UNDERSTAND THAT?

20:36.110 --> 20:37.646
<i>HURRY , HURRY'.!</i>

20:37.737 --> 20:39.273
STOP! STOP!

20:39.363 --> 20:40.569
<i>STOP! STOP!</i>

20:41.907 --> 20:43.068
<i>STOP!</i>

20:43.117 --> 20:45.108
<i>[pounding on door]</i>

20:47.455 --> 20:49.287
<i>(Ellington) PUT THIS'
