20:49.373 --> 20:52.411
<i>[pounding on door]</i>

20:52.501 --> 20:53.753
<i>[thunder]</i>

20:56.255 --> 20:58.087
<i>[suspense music]</i>

21:05.139 --> 21:07.801
<i>[suspense music intensifies]</i>

21:21.989 --> 21:23.571
<i>[thunder]</i>

21:49.934 --> 21:52.676
