FOR YOU, MY SON.

21:52.770 --> 21:54.056
ALL YOUR LIFE

21:54.146 --> 21:55.978
YOU WILL REMEMBER
THIS NIGHT

21:56.065 --> 21:59.729
AND YOU'LL KNOW,
MR. ELLINGTON

21:59.819 --> 22:01.355
WHOM YOU HAVE
TURNED LOOSE

22:01.445 --> 22:03.482
UPON THE WORLD.

22:03.531 --> 22:06.319
I, I DIDN'T
BELIEVE YOU.

22:06.408 --> 22:10.402
I, I SAVV HIM AND
DIDN'T RECOGNIZE HIM.

22:10.496 --> 22:13.033
THAT IS
MAN'S WEAKNESS

22:13.123 --> 22:15.706
